<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

17
00:01:16,020 --> 00:01:19,512
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best!</i>

18
00:01:19,590 --> 00:01:23,048
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

19
00:01:23,260 --> 00:01:27,356
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!</i>

20
00:01:42,007 --> 00:01:47,604
<i>Deadlock! Sannin Showdown!</i>

21
00:01:48,046 --> 00:01:49,445
Oh! Dad!

22
00:01:59,424 --> 00:02:00,288
This isn't good!

23
00:02:00,825 --> 00:02:03,453
Oh no, Gamatatsu!
Let's get out of here!

24
00:02:03,662 --> 00:02:05,755
What? Why, why?

25
00:02:06,031 --> 00:02:07,521
It doesn't matter, just hurry up!

26
00:02:18,009 --> 00:02:21,945
Manda and Orochimaru,
Katsuyu and Tsunade...

27
00:02:22,647 --> 00:02:25,707
They all bring back memories...

28
00:02:30,288 --> 00:02:34,725
Shall we have a reunion
or something, Jiraiya?

29
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:38,359
Fool! I summon you after a long absence

30
00:02:38,430 --> 00:02:40,728
and you make these boring jokes.

31
00:02:41,566 --> 00:02:45,024
The time to conclude this long,
fateful confrontation has come.

32
00:02:46,271 --> 00:02:49,934
I'm bringing Orochimaru down,
here and now!

33
00:02:52,677 --> 00:02:54,338
Hey Orochimaru...

34
00:02:54,913 --> 00:02:59,111
Why'd you have to summon me
to a place like this?!

35
00:03:05,056 --> 00:03:07,286
You... I'm going to eat you up!

36
00:03:07,492 --> 00:03:09,653
Don't say that, Lord Manda...

37
00:03:10,328 --> 00:03:11,727
You will be duly rewarded.

38
00:03:11,796 --> 00:03:14,594
Who said I'm talking to you?!

39
00:03:14,866 --> 00:03:18,859
Don't be so flippant, brat!

40
00:03:23,041 --> 00:03:24,668
Hey, Orochimaru...

41
00:03:24,743 --> 00:03:29,271
I expect you to prepare
a sacrificial offering of 100 people later.

42
00:03:32,784 --> 00:03:34,274
<i>Though Lord Orochimaru is</i>
<i>Manda's master,</i>

43
00:03:34,352 --> 00:03:36,912
<i>if Manda learns that Lord Orochimaru</i>
<i>can't use Jutsu,</i>

44
00:03:37,088 --> 00:03:39,215
<i>Manda will no doubt</i>
<i>double cross him.</i>

45
00:03:40,325 --> 00:03:43,726
<i>Despite the fact that he had</i>
<i>no other choice, in his condition,</i>

46
00:03:43,795 --> 00:03:46,263
<i>it was too risky for Lord Orochimaru</i>
<i>to summon Manda.</i>

47
00:03:47,032 --> 00:03:50,900
Katsuyu... take that kid to Shizune!

48
00:03:51,469 --> 00:03:53,096
Yes, ma'am.

49
00:04:04,349 --> 00:04:06,044
All right! I can fight, too!

50
00:04:09,454 --> 00:04:12,252
Shizune, please take care of this child.

51
00:04:13,792 --> 00:04:14,759
Naruto...

52
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:19,121
Also, the battle is going to get
quite vicious from now.

53
00:04:19,631 --> 00:04:24,330
Please go far away with my clone
and conceal yourself...

54
00:04:25,904 --> 00:04:28,464
That's what Lady Tsunade wants.

55
00:04:30,575 --> 00:04:31,507
<i>Lady Tsunade...</i>

56
00:04:47,292 --> 00:04:48,350
You...

57
00:04:49,094 --> 00:04:52,621
I'll hang you out until you're dry!

58
00:04:53,198 --> 00:04:57,794
I've been wanting a snakeskin wallet...

59
00:05:01,773 --> 00:05:05,675
Orochimaru,
you've sunk too deeply into vice!

60
00:05:06,044 --> 00:05:08,444
We are no longer comrades.

61
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:10,040
Comrades?

62
00:05:12,317 --> 00:05:13,909
That word makes me shiver.

63
00:05:14,285 --> 00:05:16,810
Today is the last day that
we are called Sannin!

64
00:05:34,806 --> 00:05:35,773
Acid Slime!

65
00:05:45,350 --> 00:05:46,977
I'll start with this one!

66
00:06:06,871 --> 00:06:07,860
Katsuyu!

67
00:06:07,939 --> 00:06:08,997
Lady Tsunade...

68
00:06:28,193 --> 00:06:29,057
Here they come!

69
00:06:29,127 --> 00:06:30,287
I know!

70
00:06:41,472 --> 00:06:43,201
Tsunade! Stay away!

71
00:06:43,875 --> 00:06:45,809
Bunta! Give me some oil!

72
00:06:46,077 --> 00:06:47,510
Okay!

73
00:06:51,616 --> 00:06:52,548
<i>Fire Style!</i>

74
00:06:52,617 --> 00:06:54,642
<i>Toad Oil Flamethrower!</i>

75
00:07:14,038 --> 00:07:15,869
Humph... How's that?

76
00:07:16,107 --> 00:07:17,039
Did it work?

77
00:07:22,013 --> 00:07:23,480
No, that's...

78
00:07:29,487 --> 00:07:32,820
<i>Molten skin! He shed his skin!</i>

79
00:07:38,096 --> 00:07:40,064
Bunta! Under the earth!

80
00:07:40,131 --> 00:07:41,120
What?!

81
00:07:44,602 --> 00:07:45,466
It's the tail?!

82
00:07:54,512 --> 00:07:55,342
Keep it shut!

83
00:07:58,116 --> 00:07:59,447
<i>They're Sannin, all right.</i>

84
00:07:59,517 --> 00:08:01,508
<i>Dealing with two of them is rough.</i>

85
00:08:05,290 --> 00:08:06,086
Tsunade!

86
00:08:08,126 --> 00:08:11,118
Well now, I can kill you
by wringing your neck.

87
00:08:13,364 --> 00:08:14,092
<i>My Chakra...</i>

88
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,828
<i>At this rate...</i>

89
00:08:17,435 --> 00:08:20,199
<i>Even though you say</i>
<i>you won't die in battle,</i>

90
00:08:20,538 --> 00:08:23,803
<i>you won't have a choice if</i>
<i>I rip your neck off...</i>

91
00:08:23,875 --> 00:08:25,399
<i>Right, Tsunade?</i>

92
00:08:27,045 --> 00:08:28,478
<i>How many minutes...</i>

93
00:08:28,947 --> 00:08:30,505
<i>How many seconds can I hold on...?</i>

94
00:08:33,084 --> 00:08:34,483
<i>I have to put it on the line!</i>

95
00:08:39,724 --> 00:08:40,554
Fine!

96
00:08:41,292 --> 00:08:43,783
It's about time we put an end to this!

97
00:08:46,998 --> 00:08:47,930
<i>R-Ridiculous!</i>

98
00:09:05,884 --> 00:09:07,852
Not done yet!

99
00:09:24,235 --> 00:09:25,862
Take this!

100
00:09:31,376 --> 00:09:32,274
<i>Darn it...!</i>

101
00:09:38,883 --> 00:09:40,783
<i>Lady Tsunade... Not that...!</i>

102
00:09:41,786 --> 00:09:43,845
She's reached her limit...

103
00:09:44,122 --> 00:09:45,020
No...

104
00:09:54,399 --> 00:09:55,331
<i>This guy...</i>

105
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:57,868
<i>I've hurled him around that much,</i>
<i>yet he's still...</i>

106
00:10:05,677 --> 00:10:09,545
So this is as far as you can go.

107
00:10:11,082 --> 00:10:12,140
Shut up!

108
00:10:16,755 --> 00:10:17,653
<i>Don't rest!</i>

109
00:10:18,590 --> 00:10:19,750
<i>Keep beating him.</i>

110
00:10:27,232 --> 00:10:28,631
<i>This is the battle...</i>

111
00:10:28,967 --> 00:10:30,935
<i>where I put my life on the line!</i>

112
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,771
Lord Orochimaru!

113
00:10:39,477 --> 00:10:40,535
I won't let you go!

114
00:10:41,546 --> 00:10:43,207
You will stay with me until the end!

115
00:10:47,619 --> 00:10:48,711
Take this!

116
00:11:06,638 --> 00:11:09,471
<i>I hit him and hit him.</i>
<i>Something's different...</i>

117
00:11:10,542 --> 00:11:13,534
<i>What is it?</i>
<i>This...strange sense of discomfort?</i>

118
00:11:44,175 --> 00:11:45,506
<i>However, with this...!</i>

119
00:11:50,181 --> 00:11:51,978
It's over!

120
00:12:02,861 --> 00:12:04,590
<i>He took a direct hit!</i>

121
00:12:06,798 --> 00:12:08,629
That was it.

122
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:09,789
Yeah...

123
00:12:14,439 --> 00:12:15,770
Lord Orochimaru...

124
00:12:28,052 --> 00:12:29,815
Putting me in this position!

125
00:12:30,121 --> 00:12:32,715
I want to eat you and kill you,

126
00:12:32,791 --> 00:12:36,318
but I can't even chew you up
with this hole in my mouth...

127
00:12:37,562 --> 00:12:41,054
Next time, if we meet again,
be prepared!

128
00:13:12,630 --> 00:13:13,824
Tsunade...

129
00:13:13,965 --> 00:13:20,063
Even though you won't heal me,
I still have one way.

130
00:13:27,612 --> 00:13:31,241
A way to resurrect these arms.

131
00:13:38,590 --> 00:13:42,287
The Leaf Village...
I'll destroy it... without fail.

132
00:13:45,463 --> 00:13:48,261
At that time, it would be nice
if we could meet again...

133
00:13:48,900 --> 00:13:55,328
My comrades...
Tsunade and Jiraiya.

134
00:13:57,609 --> 00:13:58,667
<i>That face...?!</i>

135
00:14:00,845 --> 00:14:04,008
<i>In some way or another,</i>
<i>he took someone else's body...?!</i>

136
00:14:05,550 --> 00:14:07,450
<i>No wonder,</i>
<i>when we went at it a while ago,</i>

137
00:14:07,518 --> 00:14:10,919
<i>I didn't get the same feeling</i>
<i>from him that I did in the past...</i>

138
00:14:15,093 --> 00:14:17,027
The true elixir of life.

139
00:14:17,295 --> 00:14:18,922
That's my...

140
00:14:19,297 --> 00:14:21,026
my immortality!

141
00:14:23,768 --> 00:14:25,235
Some day, in the future...

142
00:14:30,074 --> 00:14:30,938
Wait!

143
00:14:34,112 --> 00:14:36,910
<i>The bones in my ribs and feet</i>
<i>are broken...</i>

144
00:14:43,488 --> 00:14:45,888
<i>The side effects of the Jutsu</i>
<i>are starting...</i>

145
00:14:49,160 --> 00:14:51,151
<i>My body is...already...</i>

146
00:15:18,489 --> 00:15:22,585
Tsunade, you haven't changed.
You're no good at wagers.

147
00:15:25,697 --> 00:15:28,723
<i>The Hokage is my dream!</i>

148
00:15:29,167 --> 00:15:30,725
<i>I'll give you one week.</i>

149
00:15:31,202 --> 00:15:33,727
<i>If you can master that Jutsu,</i>

150
00:15:33,805 --> 00:15:36,273
<i>I'll acknowledge that you have</i>
<i>what it takes to become the Hokage...</i>

151
00:15:36,341 --> 00:15:38,536
<i>and give you this necklace.</i>

152
00:15:38,810 --> 00:15:40,641
<i>It's no joke!</i>

153
00:15:40,945 --> 00:15:44,142
<i>If I have three days,</i>
<i>I'll master this Jutsu!</i>

154
00:15:46,250 --> 00:15:48,081
<i>Men don't go back on their word!</i>

155
00:15:50,888 --> 00:15:54,949
<i>I'm the grandson of the Hokage who</i>
<i>built the Village Hidden in Leaves, so...!</i>

156
00:15:55,893 --> 00:15:59,192
<i>You said it.</i>
<i>Men don't go back on their word!</i>

157
00:15:59,263 --> 00:16:04,360
<i>Right! I'll become just like Grandfather.</i>
<i>And the Hokage name will be mine!</i>

158
00:16:05,737 --> 00:16:09,104
<i>Becoming the Hokage is my dream!</i>

159
00:16:13,978 --> 00:16:17,072
<i>I love this village and my comrades.</i>

160
00:16:17,682 --> 00:16:19,547
<i>So I want to protect them.</i>

161
00:16:23,187 --> 00:16:24,950
<i>An existence that protects everyone.</i>

162
00:16:27,091 --> 00:16:29,355
<i>Becoming the Hokage is my dream...</i>

163
00:16:33,564 --> 00:16:37,227
<i>I'd like you... to take this.</i>

164
00:16:44,208 --> 00:16:45,698
Any time now, the side effects...

165
00:16:46,577 --> 00:16:47,441
Lady Tsunade...

166
00:16:53,684 --> 00:16:54,776
You...

167
00:16:55,920 --> 00:17:01,017
It's nothing... If I rest a bit, I'll return
to my young form.

168
00:17:01,826 --> 00:17:03,418
I'll rest in town.

169
00:17:03,594 --> 00:17:06,791
And when Naruto wakes up,
We'll return to the Leaf Village.

170
00:17:07,331 --> 00:17:08,320
Tsunade...

171
00:17:09,834 --> 00:17:13,133
Starting now, don't call me Tsunade.
Call me...

172
00:17:14,539 --> 00:17:16,973
The Fifth Hokage?!

173
00:17:20,011 --> 00:17:24,141
Old Lady Tsunade is
the Fifth Hokage starting today...

174
00:17:24,849 --> 00:17:28,148
What, you look disgruntled, Naruto.

175
00:17:28,419 --> 00:17:31,911
After all, compared to the old man,
the Third Hokage

176
00:17:32,056 --> 00:17:33,887
there's something...

177
00:17:34,992 --> 00:17:37,825
rough natured and kind of selfish...

178
00:17:37,995 --> 00:17:40,862
Ioose with money, catty and stupid...

179
00:17:41,966 --> 00:17:46,562
Somehow, I'm going to worry
if she can do it properly.

180
00:17:47,004 --> 00:17:50,963
Lady Tsunade, would you like
to order something...

181
00:17:51,209 --> 00:17:55,305
Moreover, a 50 year old lady
transforming into a young lady...

182
00:17:56,180 --> 00:17:58,375
Is it okay for the person who
will become Hokage

183
00:17:58,449 --> 00:18:00,212
to lie to everyone, I wonder?

184
00:18:02,053 --> 00:18:03,611
Go outside, brat!

185
00:18:11,529 --> 00:18:14,987
<i>It's just like before...</i>

186
00:18:29,013 --> 00:18:32,574
Despite how I look,
I'm going to be the Fifth Hokage.

187
00:18:33,384 --> 00:18:36,285
I shouldn't take
this short brat of a foe seriously...

188
00:18:38,756 --> 00:18:40,724
This one is enough...

189
00:18:41,192 --> 00:18:43,854
Don't call me brat!

190
00:18:44,262 --> 00:18:47,959
I may be like this now,
but I'll be Hokage some day!

191
00:19:08,719 --> 00:19:09,879
Here I go!

192
00:19:19,931 --> 00:19:21,159
<i>Another brow flick?!</i>

193
00:19:45,389 --> 00:19:47,254
Become a fine man...

194
00:19:49,694 --> 00:19:52,492
<i>and, a fine Hokage.</i>

195
00:19:57,935 --> 00:19:58,731
Yeah!

196
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:14,581
Okay! Shall we go home?

197
00:20:14,652 --> 00:20:16,085
To our hometown the Leaf Village!

198
00:20:16,220 --> 00:20:19,087
What? I haven't eaten yet...!

199
00:20:21,592 --> 00:20:23,253
Don't try to distract me by laughing

200
00:20:44,115 --> 00:20:46,174
<i>Nawaki... Dan...</i>

201
00:20:51,656 --> 00:20:54,625
<i>the boy who will inherit your dreams,</i>
<i>my beloved ones,</i>

202
00:20:57,628 --> 00:20:58,993
<i>is right here!</i>

203
00:21:06,237 --> 00:21:10,936
<i>I believe your promise,</i>
<i>its a true heart give me courage</i>

204
00:21:11,009 --> 00:21:15,343
<i>Always I feel it</i>
<i>the precious time with you</i>

205
00:21:15,947 --> 00:21:19,474
<i>On your still shoulder</i>

206
00:21:20,719 --> 00:21:25,179
<i>I feel the wind that blows</i>
<i>towards tomorrow</i>

207
00:21:25,356 --> 00:21:30,794
<i>The city lights are like pieces of stars</i>

208
00:21:31,296 --> 00:21:35,596
<i>That hold us together</i>

209
00:21:36,067 --> 00:21:45,305
<i>"Each one of us glows differently,"</i>

210
00:21:45,376 --> 00:21:47,970
<i>you say laughingly</i>

211
00:21:48,213 --> 00:21:53,879
<i>but you look most dazzling</i>

212
00:21:54,452 --> 00:21:58,821
<i>Like a comet,</i>

213
00:21:58,890 --> 00:22:04,988
<i>like the rainbow after the storm</i>

214
00:22:05,063 --> 00:22:12,162
<i>You bring light into my heart</i>

215
00:22:13,171 --> 00:22:22,546
<i>Being lost can be the answer</i>

216
00:22:23,882 --> 00:22:31,414
<i>Let's promise we won't cheat</i>

217
00:22:31,489 --> 00:22:35,482
<i>Uh...like a shooting star,</i>
<i>we do go ahead.</i>

218
00:22:38,263 --> 00:22:42,097
Yahoo! Here we are
at a hot spring spot!

219
00:22:42,167 --> 00:22:46,661
While Pervy Sage is gawking at women,
and Old Lady Tsunade is out somewhere,

220
00:22:46,738 --> 00:22:48,831
I'm gonna relax and enjoy myself!

221
00:22:50,008 --> 00:22:52,738
What?! Who worked over my room?!

222
00:22:53,211 --> 00:22:55,338
I don't know who they are,

223
00:22:55,413 --> 00:23:00,146
but I'm gonna find them
and kick their butts!

224
00:23:00,819 --> 00:23:03,879
Next time: "Kidnapped!
Naruto's Hot Spring Adventure!"
